images.description: PanSTARRS image of region near spiral galaxy IC 1852, often but almost certainly misidentified as NGC 1109 and/or NGC 1112; also shown is IC 1850, which is often but probably misidentified as NGC 1111
PanSTARRS image of spiral galaxy IC 1852, often but almost certainly misidentified as NGC 1109 and/or NGC 1112, also showing WISEA J024859.80+131231.1
